Route22_Text_EarlyRivalIntro::
	.string "{RIVAL}：喂！{PLAYER}！\p"
	.string "你想要到宝可梦联盟里去？\n"
	.string "得了吧！\p"
	.string "你得到的徽章\n"
	.string "还不够吧？\p"
	.string "这样的话，\n"
	.string "守卫是不会让你通过的。\p"
	.string "顺便问一句，\n"
	.string "你的宝可梦变强了吗？$"

Route22_Text_EarlyRivalDefeat::
	.string "啊啊！\n"
	.string "你只是运气好罢了！$"

Route22_Text_EarlyRivalPostBattle::
	.string "我听说宝可梦联盟遍布\n"
	.string "很厉害的训练家。\p"
	.string "我必须想想该怎样\n"
	.string "战胜他们。\p"
	.string "你不能这样磨磨蹭蹭了，\n"
	.string "继续前进吧！$"

@ Translated in RB as "{RIVAL}: What? Why do I have 2 POKéMON? You should catch some more too!"
